================================================================================================
== Welcome to the Automatic Telescope Control System: Stargazer
================================================================================================

This is the web application that allows users to remotely schedule telescope positions.

================================================================================================
== Gems Used:
================================================================================================

# for creating initial CSS/views:
web-app-theme
http://github.com/pilu/web-app-theme

# for authentication/login subsystem:
authlogic
http://github.com/binarylogic/authlogic

# for time validation:
validates_timeliness
http://github.com/adzap/validates_timeliness
http://www.railslodge.com/plugins/1160-validates-timeliness

# for automatically creating class diagrams from Rails applications:
railroad

# for adding text field inputs for date/time:
chronic_duration

# for adding binary images to a model:
paperclip
http://github.com/binarylogic/authlogic

# astronomy picture of the day - only for testing data:
dougsko-apod

# for separate CSS/views for mobile devices:
mobile-fu
http://github.com/brendanlim/mobile-fu
http://github.com/billymeltdown/mobile-fu

# for pagination:
will_paginate
http://wiki.github.com/mislav/will_paginate

# for setting cron jobs
whenever
http://github.com/javan/whenever